      <title>马科斯抨击中国，誓言在争议海域绝不屈服</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/marcos-swipes-at-beijing-in-vow-to-not-yield-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在亚洲最高安全论坛上发表演讲时，明确宣称菲律宾对有争议的南海拥有主权，并对北京进行了尖锐批评 — — 而中国新任国防部长就坐在听众席中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/marcos-swipes-at-beijing-in-vow-to-not-yield-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
