      <title>胡塞武装称美国和英国对也门实施了迄今为止最致命的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-uk-carry-out-deadliest-strike-on-yemen-s-houthi-militants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[胡塞武装分子称，美国和英国周四对也门发动空袭，造成至少 16 人死亡，这是自今年 1 月开始阻止该组织袭击红海附近船只以来，针对该组织最惨重的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-uk-carry-out-deadliest-strike-on-yemen-s-houthi-militants</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 08:12:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
